THIRD-PARTY DATA

This project uses publicly available data from NASA's Lunar Reconnaissance
Orbiter (LRO) mission. These datasets are in the public domain and provided
by NASA's Planetary Data System (PDS):

  Diviner Lunar Radiometer Experiment (DLRE)
    Williams et al. (2019) JGR Planets — EPF dataset
    Paige et al. (2010) Science 330 — PSR temperatures

  Lunar Reconnaissance Orbiter Camera (LROC) Wide Angle Camera
    Sato et al. (2014) JGR Planets — WAC photometry

  Mini-RF Radar
    Spudis et al. (2010) Geophysical Research Letters — CPR data

  Lyman Alpha Mapping Project (LAMP)
    Gladstone et al. (2010) Science 330 — UV signatures

  LCROSS Impact Data
    Colaprete et al. (2010) Science 330 — Cabeus H₂O confirmation

  LOLA (Lunar Orbiter Laser Altimeter)
    Mazarico et al. (2011) Icarus 211 — PSR catalog

