SCIENTIFIC REFERENCES

The thermal physics model implements methods described in:
  Vasavada et al. (2012) JGR Planets — subsurface thermal profile
  Hayne et al. (2015) JGR Planets — global hydration map

Ice stability threshold (<110 K) from:
  Paige et al. (2010) Science 330

